{"id": "26406", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26406", "title": "Custerian Wristguards", "text": "Custerian Wristguards are\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". They require\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a031 to drop.\nTheir unique feature is giving player &lt;a href=\"experience\"&gt;experience&lt;/a&gt; upon looting &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt; (same amount). Although helpful at any level for at least some time, this is most usable for low-level characters, especially when it is combined with a high value of Gold Find. It is also very useful for &lt;a href=\"Paragon\"&gt;Paragon&lt;/a&gt; level farming in the &lt;a href=\"Treasure%20Realm\"&gt;Treasure Realm&lt;/a&gt;, as one will inevitably gather millions of gold, especially on higher difficulty levels.\nThe experience gained from this item is not shared to other players in the same party. The legendary effect works even if equipped on &lt;a href=\"Followers\"&gt;Followers&lt;/a&gt;."}
