{"id": "27323", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=27323", "title": "Danetta's Hatred", "text": "Danetta's Hatred\u00a0is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Reaper%20of%20Souls\"&gt;Reaper of Souls&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Demon%20Hunter\"&gt;Demon Hunter&lt;/a&gt;-only minor class\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nThis set is named for\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Danetta\"&gt;Danetta&lt;/a&gt;, one of the first Demon Hunters. It requires a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0of 60.\nPieces.\nThe set consists of just two items, both of which are required to complete the set. Both pieces are Demon Hunter-only.\nSet Bonus (2 pieces):\nThe damage bonus applies not only to the damaging skill runes of Vault (Trail of Cinders and Action Shot), but also to the clones left by Danetta's Spite (which makes the clones use Demon Hunter's skills with \"double\" their normal damage)."}
{"id": "27325", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=27325", "title": "Danetta's Revenge", "text": "Danetta's Revenge\u00a0is one of the two\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Hand%20Crossbows\"&gt;Hand Crossbows&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Danetta%27s%20Hatred\"&gt;Danetta's Hatred&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a060 to drop.\nIn addition to set bonus, it also enhances &lt;a href=\"Vault\"&gt;Vault&lt;/a&gt; by adding the Rattling Roll rune effect to any other. This is one of the few set items to have a &lt;a href=\"legendary\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; affix."}
{"id": "27327", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=27327", "title": "Danetta's Spite", "text": "Danetta's Spite\u00a0is one of the two\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Hand%20Crossbows\"&gt;Hand Crossbows&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Danetta%27s%20Hatred\"&gt;Danetta's Hatred&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a060 to drop.\nIn addition to set bonus, it also enhances &lt;a href=\"Vault\"&gt;Vault&lt;/a&gt; by making it leave a shadow clone at the original location after each use. Each clone lasts 5 seconds (can have as many as needed), draws enemy attention and uses &lt;a href=\"Demon%20Hunters\"&gt;demon hunter&lt;/a&gt; skills with 25% of original damage. This is one of the few set items with a legendary affix."}
