{"id": "30630", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30630", "title": "Gauntlets of the Rain", "text": "Gauntlets of the Rain were &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"gloves\"&gt;gloves&lt;/a&gt; to be implemented in patch 2.2.0 of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". They were expected to require &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 70 to drop. Prior to the release, they were cut and replaced with &lt;a href=\"Natalya%27s%20Touch\"&gt;Natalya's Touch&lt;/a&gt;, while the special affix has been altered and moved to the &lt;a href=\"Crashing%20Rain\"&gt;Crashing Rain&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"belt\"&gt;belt&lt;/a&gt;."}
