{"id": "28433", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=28433", "title": "Gavin the Thief", "text": "Gavin the Thief, Plaguebearer, is a &lt;a href=\"Super%20Unique\"&gt;Super Unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Brigand\"&gt;Brigand&lt;/a&gt; found in the &lt;a href=\"Hidden%20Aqueducts\"&gt;Hidden Aqueducts&lt;/a&gt; in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBiography.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231285\"&gt;1285&lt;/a&gt;, he was a companion to &lt;a href=\"Covetous%20Shen\"&gt;Covetous Shen&lt;/a&gt; in their search for the mystical crucible. However, for whatever reason Gavin knocked Shen out, locking him in a barrel afterwards, and searched for the crucible for himself. He did not notice, however, that the device has been cursed, and &lt;a href=\"The%20Nephalem\"&gt;The Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; was forced to kill Gavin, as the latter has lost his sanity.\nIn-game.\nIn combat, Gavin has Fast and Plagued affixes, and is assisted by multiple foes in the area. After his death, Shen says that now he can use the purified crucible to combine &lt;a href=\"gems\"&gt;gems&lt;/a&gt;."}
