{"id": "5598", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5598", "title": "Geleb the Flame", "text": "Geleb was a member of the &lt;a href=\"High%20Council%20of%20Zakarum\"&gt;High Council of Zakarum&lt;/a&gt; during the 13th century. Enthralled by &lt;a href=\"Mephisto\"&gt;Mephisto&lt;/a&gt;, he and his fellow council members corrupted the faith from the inside. For this, they were rewarded by Mephisto, who transformed them into &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s and gave them abilities far beyond mere &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt;s.\nIsmail and his fellow council members were slain by a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20II\"&gt;group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; when they fought their way into &lt;a href=\"Travincal\"&gt;Travincal&lt;/a&gt;. \nIn-game.\nDiablo II.\nGeleb Flamefinger is a &lt;a href=\"Super%20Unique\"&gt;Super Unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Council%20Member\"&gt;Council Member 2&lt;/a&gt; who guards the &lt;a href=\"Compelling%20Orb\"&gt;Compelling Orb&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Blackened%20Temple\"&gt;Blackened Temple&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Travincal\"&gt;Travincal&lt;/a&gt; in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeleb Flamefinger spawns with three minion Council Members. He is found in the Black Temple in Travincal along with &lt;a href=\"Ismail%20Vilehand\"&gt;Ismail Vilehand&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Toorc%20Icefist\"&gt;Toorc Icefist&lt;/a&gt;, who also spawn with minions. He can &lt;a href=\"heal\"&gt;heal&lt;/a&gt; himself and his minions and run away after taking heavy damage. Typically, players regard this fight as being much tougher than fighting Mephisto himself.\nBonuses:\nDevelopment.\nGeleb Flamefinger has an unused bloody color palette due to Council Member monsters lack of palshift.dat file and randtransform.dat file error in D2Client.dll\nDiablo IV.\nGeleb features in the fifth of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", as part of the &lt;a href=\"Fell%20Council\"&gt;Fell Council&lt;/a&gt;. He has been renamed to Geleb the Flame."}
{"id": "42342", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=42342", "title": "Geli", "text": "Geli is a resident of &lt;a href=\"Port%20Justinian\"&gt;Port Justinian&lt;/a&gt;. When the &lt;a href=\"Fetish\"&gt;Fetish&lt;/a&gt; attacked the &lt;a href=\"town\"&gt;town&lt;/a&gt;, he were among those taken prisoner; brought to the &lt;a href=\"Fetish%20Village\"&gt;Fetish Village&lt;/a&gt;. When a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; arrived in the village and killed the Fetish that remained there, Geli was among those they rescued. He told them that the rest of the survivors had been taken to the &lt;a href=\"Kikuras%20Rapids\"&gt;Kikuras Rapids&lt;/a&gt; for an unknown purpose. The hero(es) instructed Geli to head back to the port with the other survivors, while they headed to the rapids.\nIn-game.\nGeli is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is encountered in the &lt;a href=\"Fetish%20Village\"&gt;Fetish Village&lt;/a&gt; during the \"&lt;a href=\"Heart%20of%20the%20Jungle\"&gt;Heart of the Jungle&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;. He drops &lt;a href=\"Geli%27s%20Gratitude\"&gt;Geli's Gratitude&lt;/a&gt;."}
