{"id": "27382", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=27382", "title": "Golden Scourge", "text": "Golden Scourge\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Craftable%20items\"&gt;crafted&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"flails\"&gt;flail&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=\"Crusader\"&gt;Crusader&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a070 to be used.\nThe special effect does not affect the initial strike of &lt;a href=\"Smite%20%28Crusader%29\"&gt;Smite&lt;/a&gt;, but allows it to spread farther to additional enemies (but cannot hit the same enemy twice per cast). The effect is especially powerful against crowds, mostly when combined with &lt;a href=\"Armor%20of%20the%20Kind%20Regent\"&gt;Armor of the Kind Regent&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn addition, it is one of the three weapons (the others being &lt;a href=\"Skycutter\"&gt;Skycutter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Akanesh\"&gt;Akanesh&lt;/a&gt;) that can increase damage done with &lt;a href=\"Holy\"&gt;Holy&lt;/a&gt; skills.\nCrafting.\nGolden Scourge can be crafted using the\u00a0Plan: Golden Scourge, 64000 &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt;, 20 &lt;a href=\"Reusable%20Parts\"&gt;Reusable Parts&lt;/a&gt;, 20 &lt;a href=\"Arcane%20Dust\"&gt;Arcane Dust&lt;/a&gt;, 30 &lt;a href=\"Veiled%20Crystal\"&gt;Veiled Crystal&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Caldeum%20Nightshade\"&gt;Caldeum Nightshade&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Corrupted%20Angel%20Flesh\"&gt;Corrupted Angel Flesh&lt;/a&gt;.\nPrior to Patch 2.0.6., it also required one &lt;a href=\"Hilt%20of%20the%20Silver%20Wolf\"&gt;Hilt of the Silver Wolf&lt;/a&gt;, dropped from unique &lt;a href=\"Fallen%20Hound\"&gt;Fallen Hound&lt;/a&gt;s."}
