{"id": "6489", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6489", "title": "Goldskin (Diablo II)", "text": "Goldskin is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; found in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". \nAlthough its high defense and boost to resistances are useful, Goldskin's most noticeable property is its ability to double &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt; dropped by enemies. This bonus can add up, particularly later in the game; however, it is generally outclassed for higher level characters by &lt;a href=\"Skullder%27s%20Ire\"&gt;Skullder's Ire&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Wealth%20Rune%20Word\"&gt;Wealth Rune Word&lt;/a&gt;.\nStats.\nDefense: \nRequired Level: 28\nRequired Strength: 80\nDurability: 70"}
{"id": "20836", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20836", "title": "Goldskin (Diablo III)", "text": "Goldskin is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Body%20Armor\"&gt;chest armor&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;. It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 50 to drop.\nIn addition to the highest &lt;a href=\"Gold\"&gt;Gold&lt;/a&gt; Find bonus in game (outright doubling it if its the \"only\" item devoted to the stat without &lt;a href=\"Paragon\"&gt;Paragon&lt;/a&gt; levels), it also makes enemies drop gold on hit, much like &lt;a href=\"Treasure%20Goblin\"&gt;Treasure Goblins&lt;/a&gt; do. There is a limit on how often this can happen though, both per second and per enemy.\nThe legendary effect works even if equipped on &lt;a href=\"Followers\"&gt;Followers&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "6357", "revid": "52534049", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6357", "title": "Goldstrike Arch", "text": "Goldstrike Arch is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Gothic%20Bow\"&gt;Gothic Bow&lt;/a&gt;.\nAlthough its bonuses may seem lackluster, its enhanced damage to &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;Demons&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; pays off, as there aren't many enemies that are neither.\nIf &lt;a href=\"Upgrading\"&gt;upgraded&lt;/a&gt;, Goldstrike Arch is one of the best options for &lt;a href=\"Bowazon\"&gt;Bowazon&lt;/a&gt;s in terms of damage output, along with the &lt;a href=\"Faith%20Rune%20Word\"&gt;Faith Rune Word&lt;/a&gt; and .\nStats.\nTwo-Hand Damage: 30 to (150-175)\nRequired Level: 46\nRequired &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;: 95\nRequired &lt;a href=\"Dexterity\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;: 118\nBow Class - "}
