{"id": "16185", "revid": "43924158", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16185", "title": "Horadric Scroll", "text": "The Horadric Scroll is a &lt;a href=\"Quest%20Items\"&gt;quest item&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"The%20Secret%20of%20the%20Vizjerei\"&gt;Act II&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;. It is first found inside a golden chest, hidden within the &lt;a href=\"Sewers%20%28Act%20II%29\"&gt;sewers&lt;/a&gt; beneath &lt;a href=\"Lut%20Gholein\"&gt;Lut Gholein&lt;/a&gt; and guarded by &lt;a href=\"Radament\"&gt;Radament&lt;/a&gt;. Picking up the Scroll initiates &lt;a href=\"The%20Horadric%20Staff%20%28quest%29\"&gt;The Horadric Staff (quest)&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe player is tasked with showing the scroll to &lt;a href=\"Deckard%20Cain\"&gt;Deckard Cain&lt;/a&gt;, who, as the last living &lt;a href=\"Horadrim\"&gt;Horadrim&lt;/a&gt;, has the knowledge to translate the ancient Horadric Runes. The Scroll relates the story of &lt;a href=\"Baal\"&gt;Baal&lt;/a&gt;'s imprisonment within &lt;a href=\"Tal%20Rasha%27s%20Tomb\"&gt;Tal Rasha's Tomb&lt;/a&gt; and provides clues as to where the player might find the components needed for restoring an Horadric Staff.\nAfter the dialogue with Cain, the Scroll disappears from the player's inventory."}
