{"id": "2472", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2472", "title": "Hratli", "text": "Hratli is an NPC from \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\", &lt;a href=\"The%20Infernal%20Gate\"&gt;Act III&lt;/a&gt;. Functions as an &lt;a href=\"armor\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"weapons\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt; vendor; he specializes in crafting and enchanting wares. He first greets the Player at the docks of Kurast. An intelligent and insightful man, he is renowned for his \"gallows humor\".\nHratli will greet the player upon their arrival at the Docks and give them a rundown of the situation, explaining that they are under assault by the forces of Mephisto and that the enchantment keeping the Docks safe might not last much longer. Later on, Hratli will move to his forge, in the lower right corner of the Docks, past the marketplace where &lt;a href=\"Natalya\"&gt;Natalya&lt;/a&gt; is stationed.\nDialogue.\nGossip about Hratli.\nSome of the other locals give their thoughts concerning Hratli."}
