{"id": "39104", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39104", "title": "Hurricane (Diablo IV)", "text": "Tornado\u00a0is a Wrath Storm skill used by\u00a0\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", based on the &lt;a href=\"Hurricane\"&gt;classic spell&lt;/a&gt; of the same name.\nIn-game.\nSimilar to its predecessor, this skill forms a semi-passive damage aura of short duration around the Druid that deals high damage over time to nearby foes. It follows the caster around and can be held on about 50% of the time relative to its cooldown.\nUsing this skill will transform the Druid back into Human form. However, once cast, it will continue to damage enemies around the Druid even if they shapeshift into a &lt;a href=\"Werewolf\"&gt;Werewolf&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a href=\"Werebear\"&gt;Werebear&lt;/a&gt;."}
