{"id": "38700", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38700", "title": "Ice Shards", "text": "Ice Shards\u00a0is a Destruction Cold spell used by\u00a0 in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIn-game.\nWhen cast, spreads 5 bolts of ice that each can deal damage to a single target, with random spread (only the central shard flies where targeted). While the shards' damage is relatively low, even considering the cheap &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt; cost and no &lt;a href=\"cooldown\"&gt;cooldown&lt;/a&gt;, they are very cost-efficient against previously Frozen foes.\nNote that this spell does \"not\" &lt;a href=\"Chill\"&gt;Chill&lt;/a&gt; / Freeze enemies by itself and must rely on other spells. It is also of very arguable efficiency if paired with &lt;a href=\"Endless%20Winter\"&gt;Endless Winter&lt;/a&gt; talent due to drastically reducing available sources of Freeze."}
