{"id": "43328", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43328", "title": "Idahir", "text": "Idahir is an &lt;a href=\"angel\"&gt;angel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; seen in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBiography.\nIdahir was part of a group of angel sentinels led by &lt;a href=\"Verathiel\"&gt;Verathiel&lt;/a&gt;. They discovered the &lt;a href=\"Realm%20of%20Damnation\"&gt;Realm of Damnation&lt;/a&gt; as it was taking shape. Cut off from the &lt;a href=\"High%20Heavens\"&gt;High Heavens&lt;/a&gt;, they carved out a &lt;a href=\"the%20Last%20Vestige\"&gt;foothold&lt;/a&gt; in the realm, battling &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s over the eons.\nWhispering Bones.\nSometime after the fall of &lt;a href=\"Skarn\"&gt;Skarn&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Class%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero(es)&lt;/a&gt; asked for his help to destroy a demonic skull that was attracting nearby &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s and was being held at bay by a &lt;a href=\"Tassi\"&gt;friend&lt;/a&gt;. Unfortunately, the friend had been enthralled into wearing the skull and was possessed by it. Luckily, they were able to safely subdue her and destroy the skull.\nLocally Sourced.\nWhen a &lt;a href=\"Vestige%20Guardian\"&gt;Vestige Guardian&lt;/a&gt; fell protecting the northern entrance of &lt;a href=\"The%20Last%20Vestige\"&gt;The Last Vestige&lt;/a&gt; from a demon horde, Idahir employed the help of the hero(es) to gather materials for him to build a gate.\nIn-game.\nIdahir is the blacksmith in &lt;a href=\"The%20Last%20Vestige\"&gt;The Last Vestige&lt;/a&gt;. He uses his hammer both for smithing and as a weapon."}
