{"id": "16062", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16062", "title": "Fly", "text": "Fly is an ability commonly used by the &lt;a href=\"Vulture%20Demon\"&gt;Vulture Demon&lt;/a&gt; class of monsters. They fly up into the air where they are immune to damage for a short period of time, after which, landing once again.\nWhile in flight, the demonic birds can pass over some barriers such as cliffs and even the walls of a house.\nWhen used by &lt;a href=\"bosses\"&gt;bosses&lt;/a&gt;, it normally ends in a &lt;a href=\"Divebomb\"&gt;Divebomb&lt;/a&gt;. Otherwise it is used to introduce an intermission phase in a boss battle.\nThis ability is similar to &lt;a href=\"Burrow\"&gt;Burrow&lt;/a&gt;, only oppositely so."}
