{"id": "49742", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49742", "title": "Forged in Battle", "text": "Forged in Battle is an &lt;a href=\"Event%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;event&lt;/a&gt; found in &lt;a href=\"The%20Keep%20Depths\"&gt;The Keep Depths&lt;/a&gt; Level 1 in &lt;a href=\"Act%20III%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act III&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". A &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt; may be offered to complete it.\n&lt;a href=\"The%20Nephalem\"&gt;The Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; must defend &lt;a href=\"Ironsmith%20Maldonado\"&gt;Ironsmith Maldonado&lt;/a&gt; as he forges new weapons for &lt;a href=\"Bastion%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Bastion's Keep&lt;/a&gt; soldiers. Over 43 seconds, several dozen Blazing Swordwielder &lt;a href=\"skeleton\"&gt;skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s will leap from the molten ore surrounding his foundry and attack. They are fairly slow and target the Nephalem rather than the Ironsmith, so they can be handled as easily as any monster pack. About 10 seconds before the end of the timer, the &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Monsters\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; skeleton &lt;a href=\"Boneripper%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Boneripper&lt;/a&gt; will leap out and attack. At the end of the timer, any remaining monsters must be killed.\nCompleting the event awards gold and experience.\nTips.\nMaldonado's foundry is found near the stairway to The Keep Depths Level 2. In &lt;a href=\"Adventure%20Mode\"&gt;Adventure Mode&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"waypoint\"&gt;waypoint&lt;/a&gt; to Level 2 usually provides faster access to the event than from Level 1 (which is the one marked on the bounty map). After using the Level 2 waypoint, ascend the stairs to Level 1 and proceed from there."}
