{"id": "36392", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=36392", "title": "Forgotten Well", "text": "Forgotten Well is a dungeon found in the &lt;a href=\"Shrouded%20Moors\"&gt;Shrouded Moors&lt;/a&gt; in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nClearing it can be nominated a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe well is a waterlogged cave, relatively small, but with lots of branches. It is filled with hordes of &lt;a href=\"Skeleton\"&gt;Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"Skeleton%20Archer\"&gt;Skeleton Archer&lt;/a&gt;s.\nIts unique feature is that it's extremely dark, so that the character is barely able to see more than a few yards ahead. &lt;a href=\"Vidian\"&gt;Daivin&lt;/a&gt; will refuse to come down if taken to the well, letting &lt;a href=\"the%20Nephalem\"&gt;the Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; explore it alone."}
