{"id": "6416", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6416", "title": "Frostburn (Diablo II)", "text": "Frostburn is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; pair of .\nAlong with , Frostburn is a pair of &lt;a href=\"gloves\"&gt;gloves&lt;/a&gt; directed towards spellcaster use. While Magefist gives a large boost to &lt;a href=\"mana\"&gt;mana&lt;/a&gt; regeneration, Frostburn gives a very large boost to mana itself (which stacks with other items that give a percentage-based increase of mana). For most casters (especially &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Skills\"&gt;fire-based&lt;/a&gt;), is arguably better, as it increases &lt;a href=\"FCR\"&gt;cast rate&lt;/a&gt;, which Frostburn lacks. The notable exception is \"mana tank\" &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=\"Energy%20Shield\"&gt;Energy Shield&lt;/a&gt;-based), which will make use of Frostburn's massive mana bonus.\nStats.\nDefense: 47-49\nRequired Level: 29\nRequired &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;: 60\nDurability: 24"}
