{"id": "26449", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26449", "title": "Fulminator", "text": "Fulminator\u00a0is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0sword in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\", one of the five &lt;a href=\"Quinblades\"&gt;Quinblades&lt;/a&gt;. It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a031 to drop.\nIt's unique property causes enemies\u00a0to crackle with lightning bolts, hitting all other enemies within a ~10 yard radius of the target on which it triggered. Affected targets do not take damage from the effect themselves.\nBecause the elements of your chosen skills override any elemental damage properties on weapons, Fulminator's unique property will only function when using skills that deal Lightning damage. It's inherent Lightning damage cannot trigger the property\u00a0when using skills of a different element."}
