{"id": "2624", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2624", "title": "Garda", "text": "Garda was the wife of &lt;a href=\"Ogden\"&gt;Ogden&lt;/a&gt; and co-owner of the &lt;a href=\"Tavern%20of%20the%20Rising%20Sun\"&gt;Tavern of the Rising Sun&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nGarda and Ogden purchased their tavern in &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231259\"&gt;1259&lt;/a&gt;, not long before the &lt;a href=\"Darkening%20of%20Tristram%20%28Event%29\"&gt;Darkening of Tristram&lt;/a&gt;. Due to the amount of coin they'd invested, they did not have the money to leave, even as things got worse.\nWhen the town's wells became stagnant, she told &lt;a href=\"Gillian\"&gt;Gillian&lt;/a&gt; that it was too dangerous to drink from them.\nThough &lt;a href=\"Aidan\"&gt;Aidan&lt;/a&gt; defeated &lt;a href=\"Diablo\"&gt;Diablo&lt;/a&gt;, in so doing, he damned Tristram. After his departure, &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s descended upon the town, killing almost all present, presumably including Garda."}
